<br>
Example - VS raid posted 3/31 was preparing our troops when we were &quot;informed&quot; that CW was going to make an attempt if we didn't hurry up. My answer.... get stuffed.<br>
<br>
Not to be rude or inconsiderate, but you don't set my timetable. If I want to sit and watch VS for 4 hours before I kill him - it is my business. If we fail 100 times before we succeed, it is still our camp.<br>
<br>
***SPECIAL NOTE*** - I had spoke to Tarin during the raid and the matter was cleared up peacefully and beneficially to both guilds. This is not a flame!<br>
<br>
To think for one minute that you have any say over another Guild or their interest in foolish. We post here (and EQ Raids) as a form of consideration and respect. To keep others from downtime and wasted manpower.<br>
<br>
Continue with your &quot;rules&quot; as you see fit. But the reputation you build with other Guilds now will follow you far into the future. My 2 cp.....<br>
